	"description": "Two years ago, I started to learn and use React. And today I&#x27;m still using it at\nmy day job as a Software Developer and in my own side projects.\n\nDuring that time I&#x27;ve come across a lot of &quot;typical&quot; issues. So I searched\naround and found some best practices that I&#x27;ve integrated into my workflow, and\nI&#x27;ve come up with things that have made my life or my team members&#x27; lives\neasier. \n\nI also faced challenges along the way that I didn&#x27;t solve in the best way at the\ntime, and I want to approach them ",
